Sparklines,as,defined,by,Tufte,are,intense,simple,word,sized,graphics,I,found,them,fascinating,and,useful,and,needed,a,way,to,generate,them,At,first,I,published,some,simple,Python,scripts,to,produce,Sparklines,but,since,then,I,have,added,this,page,for,interactively,designing,them,a,web,service,you,can,use,to,add,them,to,your,own,site,and,finally,the,source,code,to,the,web,service